init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She’s been dating a guy who’s a little too perfect, and he’s a little too interested in her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She begins to suspect something is up, and she’s right.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She succeeds, and he reveals himself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She wants to know how he knows about her secret.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yeah, you were sitting next to me, and you took them off to clean them, and you accidentally dropped them in the popcorn."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm a shapeshifter," he says, "I can change into anyone I want.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Claire has been dating the same guy over and over again, and he's been trying to get it right.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's been trying to get her to fall in love with him, and he's been trying to get her to marry him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's been trying to get her to stay with him forever, but she's always left him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm glad you're finally seeing the real me," he replies.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'll be there in a minute," he says.
